3. [api/index.php](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/api/index.php) - Login query fix
4. [Login.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/ldm_test/src/pages/Login.tsx) - Username field + token storage
5. [AuthContext.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/ldm_test/src/context/AuthContext.tsx) - Auth check logic
6. All frontend files - URL updates (16 files)

